msgstr "ハットと親プロファイルの関係性について"

#. Tag: para
#: apparmor_changehat.xml:565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The profile <filename>^adminer</filename> is only available in the context "
"of a process running under the parent profile <filename>usr.sbin.httpd2-"
"prefork</filename> ."
